       = Fred and Barney are assigned to guard a movie set which is a cover for a staged robbery planned by the actors.\n| LineColor           = FFD700\n}}\n|}\n\n==Pebbles, Dino and Bamm-Bamm==\nThis was a Flintstones-themed adaptation of the \"mystery-solving teens and a pet\" format popularized by ''[[Scooby-Doo]]'' and its various spin-offs in the 1970s (including Captain Caveman's original show on ABC). In this series, [[Pebbles Flintstone|Pebbles]] and [[Bamm-Bamm Rubble|Bamm-Bamm]] (similar, yet aged down a little, from their appearance in ''[[The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show]]'') with pet dinosaur [[Dino (The Flintstones)|Dino]] solve mysteries in the city of [[Bedrock (The Flintstones)|Bedrock]]. They would sometimes be accompanied by pals Penny, Wiggy and Moonrock.\n\n====Season 1 (1980\u201381)====\n{| class=wikitable style=\"background:#FFFFFF\"\n|- style=\"color:#FFFFFF\"\n! style=\"background:#B11030; width:20px\"| {{Abbr|N\u00ba|Number}}\n! style=\"background:#B11030; width:20px\"| {{Abbr|Ep|Episode}}\n! style=\"background:#B11030;| Title\n! style=\"background:#B11030; width:135px\"| Original air date\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 1\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 1\n| Title               = The Ghost Sitters\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1980|11|22}}\n| ShortSummary        = Pebbles, Bamm-Bamm and Dino babysit little Bratrock in a house that is haunted by the ghost of Bronco Billy.\n| LineColor           = B11030\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 2\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 2\n| Title               = Secret of Scary Valley\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1980|11|29}}\n| ShortSummary        = Pebbles, Bamm-Bamm and Dino are chased by a UFO and aliens through the rose-covered terrain of Scary Valley.\n| LineColor           = B11030\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 3\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 3\n| Title               = The Witch of the Wardrobe\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1980|12|6}}\n| ShortSummary        =